757
00:59:28,490 --> 00:59:29,530
Pohyb.

758
00:59:30,090 --> 00:59:31,660
Vľavo. Vpred.

759
00:59:36,460 --> 00:59:37,530
Je to tu.

760
00:59:38,130 --> 00:59:39,130
